{"tid":2066591,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"執到隻受左傷嘅麻雀，求各精靈訓練員入","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T01:22:33.000Z","uid":96628,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"93b043516b44251b8015569d94787af2ba931334","tid":2066591,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"佢受左傷飛唔起<br />\n我見到佢嗰陣應該喺到徘徊左一段時間<br />\n可能係早兩日落雨令佢受傷<br />\n有冇人知可以比咩佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢驚到唔敢郁<br />\n屎都痾左篤，幫佢清左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTrTXyg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTrTXyg.png&h=df46b28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDKaZMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDKaZMJ.png&h=7fef85cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zj6ArrP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzj6ArrP.png&h=b1ca719b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/85/89/a1/8589a1e990aaddef3479e1574c617f33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F85%2F89%2Fa1%2F8589a1e990aaddef3479e1574c617f33.png&h=d8c473e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望佢早日康復變成大比鳥飛反去大自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d100686544b502f924212c24a35ac79717eb6624","tid":2066591,"uid":155818,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"樓主會中禽流感先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f61e27f00503793eb12eb7f8f1c9f85cca7b7d","tid":2066591,"uid":86395,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"h5n1<br />\n樓豬rip"},{"pid":"6da79b